Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是“泥华留斗”的总长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是狂犬 狂犬泽村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小弟好像受了你们不少招待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份礼我得要好好回应才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我这恶魔的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真不愧是泽村老大 太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要找我来帮忙的话 就挑些更厉害的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有欺负弱小的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 请跟我交往好吗 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.70,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我已经有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三振出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束 哈里斯塔夫第二十一 连败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这第二十一次连败…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喽唆 才第二十次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周同一时间请继续收看游星少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 泽村正治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在没有女友的情况下渡过了十七年又两个月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续二十次失恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今纪录持续刷新中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一份大碗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！ 你们少在我面前卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每个人都是这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了别叫我大哥哥了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到马子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管 走开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来当你的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真空虚 太空虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想交个平凡的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与她共度平凡甜蜜的校园生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打架再怎么强也没任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围的人都怕我 就连女生也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是高中三年都交不到女友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能把右手当女朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样灰暗的青春真是太悲惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们一直做个朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁都好 来当我的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 刚刚的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会幻听 看来这次伤的可真严重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又 又听到女孩子的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音更清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头 头好晕… 牧绘小姐 快拿药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 冷静下来正治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么玩意啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天 右手的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的 你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的袖口会有女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是正治 这不是作梦 真的是正治耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 为什么我会在正治的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想问你 为什么右手会有胸部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 会有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 为什么你会认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我… 一直都在暗恋着你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗… 暗恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从三年前第一眼看见就喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在想如果能跟正治在一起该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是我有生以来第一次被人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这一点也不值得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被右手告白一点也不值得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是暗恋还是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说白点这样让我很困扰 我手变这样你叫我怎么生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话 话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是醒了过来就在你的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:09:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道原因 其实我也是害怕到想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能够在心爱的正治身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也有些开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿个头 我可是一点都不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被称为“狂犬泽村”令人畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 我宰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是不伦不类了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力让别人害怕助你一臂之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这家伙的实体又怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂志还是收在同一个地方比较好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的报纸跟杂志也都成为文明垃圾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为有些凌乱 所以我想整理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好像也不坏嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小… 小奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床底下也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都丢掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要任意决定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你家在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去你家的话就有可能知道你为什会变成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不想变回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大 昨天真是多谢啦… 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是忙着打架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏他不在 今天终于能够清静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 班长 跟我来办公室拿参考资料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 傲慢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玛琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鸟 美鸟！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这是你家？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好大!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个千金大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我看还是回去吧 我觉得这样子也没什么不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是贵府小姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐有事外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天可能回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大会是感冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探病看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宫原同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸭葱女高的小姐们找我有何贵事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我们是泽村的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你就在这里 却说另一个你外出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了 这下真的糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为能跟最喜欢的正治在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是在月台上看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一直都只是在很远的地方看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小仓桥高中的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是大小姐 还是个优等生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们都听说正治是樱田门高中的不良而感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道 其实是个很温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在帮助弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢那样的正治了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在我非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 昨天真是太感谢了 今天是怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 只是有点小感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去探望一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大 现在我们就过去探望你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么大不了的 我没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我现在可是跟崇拜你的女孩子在一起噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人说要过去探望你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样 那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎么喜欢我 我还是不会喜欢上变成右手的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我觉得很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渴望的是人类的女友而不是右手的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对不要出声 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 宫原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要猛按门铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是优子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是由香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆哓 全中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢 我是泽村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒不要紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫原那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去便利商店买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 先进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母在国外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有个姐姐 不过一直待在男友那很少回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次我们做饭给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请品尝我们做的 满怀爱意的高丽菜肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆哓 满怀爱的高丽菜肉卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 洗手间在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 走廊左边转角就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫原那家伙怎么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您喜欢年纪比自己还小的女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您现在好像没有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆哓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了 沉寂了十七年又两个月 我的春天终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪比我小的 我也交往了二十个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 可以吻你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 怎么这么大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞 请闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 泽村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是“泥华留斗”的女成员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来替被你打进医院的男友报仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 你有没有在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来 泽村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然敢… 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 就用这个一刀解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 请饶过我们一命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治才是 没事吧 有没有受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 刚才我晕了过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我守住约定了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有发出声音噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直都在暗恋着正治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美鸟 我叫春日野美鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 美鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 像这时候就别管什么约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出个声通知我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果我的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 那到时候再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让女孩子受伤 这样的守密也没任何意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然变成了我的右手 但你好歹也是个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢正治了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽村老大 你不要紧吧 刚刚那些女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 放手 离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样跟最喜欢的正治在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在依然就像是在作梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是作为女友而只是右手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人有些遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果这秘密在这世上只有我们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想的话 我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次在正治的房里看到的月亮非常的漂亮
